<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 18:17:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>意大利总理梅洛尼本周将访华并提出贸易和投资议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</link><description>一位参与计划的人士告诉路透社，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼将于7月26日至31日访问中国，这是她上任以来的首次访问，旨在改善与中国的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>Moncler 营业利润超出预期，亚洲收入增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/italys-moncler-posts-11-increase-first-half-revenues-boosted-by-asia-2024-07-24/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Moncler 今年上半年的营业利润超出了分析师的预期，部分原因是该公司在亚洲的业绩带动了收入增长 11%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/italys-moncler-posts-11-increase-first-half-revenues-boosted-by-asia-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国希望增强菲律宾在其水域作业的能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-looking-bolster-philippines-ability-operate-its-waters-2024-07-24/</link><description>白宫高级官员周三在两国国防部长和外交部长会议之前表示，美国正在寻求增强菲律宾在其水域合法活动的能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-looking-bolster-philippines-ability-operate-its-waters-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国对帮助朝鲜的中国网络实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</link><description>美国财政部表示，美国周三对一家帮助朝鲜发展弹道导弹和太空计划的中国网络实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:33:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>奥的斯因中美建筑活动放缓下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</link><description>由于北美和中国对其新设备的需求疲软，电梯制造商奥的斯环球公司 (Otis Worldwide) 周三下调了 2024 年净销售额预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>特使表示，日本将恢复对斯里兰卡停滞项目的资助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-resume-funding-stalled-projects-sri-lanka-envoy-says-2024-07-24/</link><description>东京驻斯里兰卡特使周三表示，日本将恢复为斯里兰卡所有陷入停滞的项目提供资金，这是该岛国与其官方债权人敲定 100 亿美元重组协议以来的首次此类声明。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-resume-funding-stalled-projects-sri-lanka-envoy-says-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度可能放松对部分中国投资的限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</link><description>两位政府消息人士称，印度可能会放松对中国在太阳能电池板和电池制造等非敏感行业投资的限制，新德里缺乏专业知识，这阻碍了国内制造业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：高收益酒吧，哈里斯民意调查上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，中国比亚迪在新加坡和东南亚的电动汽车市场上扩大了对特斯拉的领先优势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</link><description>政府数据显示，今年上半年，中国比亚迪在新加坡扩大了对特斯拉的销量领先优势，凸显了这家全球最大电动汽车制造商在中国竞争对手销量方面面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>雷米首席财务官表示，尚未给出对中国白兰地调查做出决定的日期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</link><description>在顶级干邑生产商上周参加了有关该问题的听证会后，人头马君度首席财务官周三表示，北京方面尚未给出对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查做出决定的官方时间表。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯指责美国加剧北极紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</link><description>俄罗斯周三指责华盛顿加剧北极紧张局势，并驳斥了美国军方关于俄罗斯和中国在该地区加强合作可能影响地区稳定的说法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称与北京就南海问题达成“安排”，但没有对船只进行检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</link><description>一名高级安全官员周三表示，菲律宾已与北京就向南海搁浅海军舰艇上的士兵执行补给任务达成协议，但不会接受中国的检查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:35:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰告诉中国，如果莫斯科真诚行事，它愿意进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</link><description>乌克兰最高外交官周三在南部城市广州举行的会谈中告诉中国外交部长，如果莫斯科愿意真诚地进行谈判，基辅愿意与俄罗斯进行会谈，但他表示目前没有看到任何证据。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国详细介绍了扩大国家机密的法律，着眼于数据安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国本周公布了修订后的《国家秘密法》的细节，该法改变了对政府官员处理机密信息的限制，禁止负责掌握国家秘密的人员未经批准出国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:40:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷下半年力争恢复产量并应对供应链风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</link><description>保时捷周三表示，在经历了数月的供应链障碍、电动汽车需求放缓以及中国销量下滑之后，该公司正在努力恢复产量，并重新调整支出优先顺序，以打造更灵活的产品线。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>